  <text>
    <body>
      <entry xml:id="entry_næwæg" xml:lang="os" abv:completeness="russian-questions">
        <form type="lemma"><orth>næwæg</orth></form>
        <sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
            <q>новый</q>
          </abv:tr><note type="comment">; употребительны также стяженные формы и. <w>nōg</w>,
              <w>nwōg</w></note></sense>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>nōgæj</orth><form type="variant"
            ><orth>næwægæj</orth></form></form>
          <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">снова</q>
            </tr></sense>
        </re>
        <re xml:lang="os-x-iron">
          <form type="lemma"><usg><lang/></usg><orth>nōǵy</orth></form>
          <sense><sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
                <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">еще</q>
              </tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                <q>снова</q>
              </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                <q>опять</q>
              </abv:tr></sense></sense>
        </re>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>nōǵydær</orth></form>
          <sense>id.</sense>
        </re>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>nōg kænyn</orth></form>
          <sense><sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
                <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">возобновлять</q>
              </tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                <q>обновлять</q>
              </abv:tr></sense></sense>
        </re>
        <note type="comment">; ант. <ref type="xr" target="#entry_zærond"/></note>
        <exampleGrp xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict">
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">fæcæwync wæm <oRef>næwæg</oRef> bontæ</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">идут к вам новые дни (= <q>дни Нового
                года</q>)</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/>
              <biblScope>109</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">abon <oRef>næwæg</oRef> az ærcydī</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">сегодня наступил Новый год</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Коста"/>
              <biblScope>236</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">avd fæltæry syn sæ ʒawmatæ
                <oRef>næwægæj</oRef>
              <oRef>næwægmæ</oRef> ærdavy</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">семь смен одежды от новой к новой она им
                приносит</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭп."/>
              <biblScope>35</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><oRef>nwōg</oRef> carm ærzadīs Mukarajæn jæ
              særyl, æтæ ægasæj bazzadī</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">новая кожа наросла на голове у Мукара, и он
                остался жив</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭ"/>
              <biblScope>I 36</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">тæ zærond k˳yræt <oRef>næwægæj</oRef>
              raīvton</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">я сменил старый бешмет на новый</q>
            </tr>
          </example>
          <example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
            <usg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><lang/></usg>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">zarun ǧær æта fænduri caǧd
                <oRef>næwægæj</oRef> iscudæncæ</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">звуки пения и игры на фандуре снова
                раздались</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Iræf"/>
              <biblScope>120</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
            <usg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><lang/></usg>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Kurdalægon dær babæj (læʒæg)
                <oRef>næwægæj</oRef> kænun bajdædta</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Курдалагон опять взялся за изготовление
                (палки)</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Диг._сказ."/>
              <biblScope>16</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
            <usg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><lang/></usg>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">tawæræqgænæg Totaj... æ lolæ
                <oRef>næwægæj</oRef> isasuǧta</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">рассказчик Тотай снова зажег свою трубку</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MD"/>
              <biblScope>1956 VII 55</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
            <usg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><lang/></usg>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><oRef>пæwægæj</oRef> babæj wæd
              iʒuluncæ</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">и снова они веселятся (пируют)</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ОЭп."/>
              <biblScope>63<hi rendition="#rend_subscript">366</hi></biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
          <example>
            <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">aly xatt q˳yddag <oRef>ysnōg</oRef>
              kænys</quote>
            <tr xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">ты каждый раз возобновляешь дело ( =
                разговор)</q>
            </tr>
            <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Брит."/>
              <biblScope>12</biblScope></bibl>
          </example>
        </exampleGrp>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>nōg  ḱynʒ</orth><form type="variant"><orth>næwæg
              ḱynʒ</orth></form></form>
          <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">молодая невестка</q>
            </tr></sense>
          <exampleGrp xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict">
            <example>
              <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">qwamæ <oRef>nōg ḱynʒy</oRef> fyccag æxsæv
                ældaræn fenyn kodtajkkoj</quote>
              <tr xml:lang="ru">
                <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">они должны были молодую невестку в первую
                  ночь показать князю</q>
              </tr>
              <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Сека"/>
                <biblScope>10</biblScope></bibl>
            </example>
            <example>
              <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">dymgæ... wyngtæ amærzy xorz
                  <oRef>næwæg</oRef> ḱynʒaw</quote>
              <tr xml:lang="ru">
                <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">ветер подметает улицы, как хорошая молодая
                  невестка</q>
              </tr>
              <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Niger"/>
                <biblScope>81</biblScope></bibl>
            </example>
          </exampleGrp>
        </re>
        <re>
          <re>
            <?oxy_comment_start author="Vados" timestamp="20220604T154221+0300" comment="Не выставляется тире между разными re"?>
            <form type="lemma" xml:lang="os-x-iron"><?oxy_comment_end?><orth>nōgg˳yrd</orth></form>
            <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>næwægigurd</orth></form>
            <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
                <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">новорожденный</q>
              </tr></sense>
            <exampleGrp xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict">
              <example>
                <quote xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><oRef>nōgg˳yrdæn</oRef> yskodtoj
                  ḱyryngond</quote>
                <tr xml:lang="ru">
                  <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">для новорожденного сделали сундучок</q>
                </tr>
                <bibl xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Нарт._сказ."/>
                  <biblScope>313</biblScope></bibl>
              </example>
            </exampleGrp>
          </re>
        </re>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>nōgzad</orth></form>
          <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <note type="comment" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">(о самках животных) </note>
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">недавно принесшая приплод</q>
            </tr></sense>
        </re>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>nōgʒyd (kærdæg, talatæ)</orth></form>
          <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">свежий</q>
            </tr><note type="comment"> (о траве, побегах и т. п.)</note></sense>
        </re>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>nōg хаbar</orth></form>
          <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">новость</q>
            </tr></sense>
        </re>
        <re>
          <form type="lemma"><orth>Nōgbon</orth></form>
          <sense><tr xmlns="http://ossetic-studies.org/ns/abaevdict" xml:lang="ru">
              <q xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Новый год</q>
            </tr></sense>
        </re>
        <etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит к <mentioned xml:lang="os"><w type="rec"
              >nava-<?oxy_comment_start author="Vados" timestamp="20220604T165853+0300" comment="Это осетинская реконструкция?"?>ka<?oxy_comment_end?>-</w></mentioned>
          от <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/>
            <w type="rec">nava-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ine"><lang/>
            <w type="rec">newo</w></mentioned>. Представлено едва ли не во всех иранских и
          индоевропейских языках: <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
            <w>naw</w>, <w>nō</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ttt"><lang/>
            <w>nüg</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pal"><lang/>
            <w>nawak</w>, <w>nōk</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="xpr"><lang/>
            <w>nawāg</w>, <w>nawag</w>
            <gloss><q>новый</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="xpr"><w>nawag-nawag</w>
            <gloss><q>все новый и новый</q></gloss>
            <note type="comment">(= <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                <phr>næwægæj næwægmæ</phr></mentioned>)</note>
            <note type="bibl">(<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Henning._BBB"/>
                <biblScope>112</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ku"><lang/>
            <w>nu</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="x-balochi"><lang>бел.</lang>
            <w>nōk</w>, <w>nōx</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="prc"><lang/>
            <w>nö</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
            <w>nawai</w> (← <w>nawaka-</w>)</mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ydg"><lang/>
            <w>nowoγo</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sgh"><lang/>
            <w>naw</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="isk"><lang/>
            <w>nawůk</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sgy"><lang/>
            <w>nuwōk</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="yah"><lang/>
            <w>nug</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="yai"><lang/>
            <w>nava</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
            <w type="rec">nawāk</w>, <w type="rec">nawā</w> (<w>nwʼkw</w>, <w>nwʼ</w>)</mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="sog-x-man"><lang/>
            <w>nwy</w> (<w type="rec">nawaka-</w>) <gloss><q>новый</q></gloss></mentioned>,
            <mentioned xml:lang="zkh"><lang>хорезм.</lang>
            <w>nawak</w> (<phr>nawak māh</phr><note type="comment"> = <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                <phr>næwæg mæj</phr>
                <gloss><q>молодой месяц</q></gloss></mentioned></note>)<note type="bibl">
                  (<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_BSOAS"/>
                <biblScope>1971 XXXIV 318</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
            <w>nūvara</w>
            <gloss><q>свежий</q></gloss>, <gloss><q>юный</q></gloss>
            <note type="comment">(из <mentioned xml:lang="ine"><w type="rec"
                >nautara-</w></mentioned><?oxy_comment_start author="Vados" timestamp="20220604T171528+0300" comment="Это индоевропейские рексонструкции?"?>
              или от <mentioned xml:lang="ine"><w type="rec"
              >nava-</w></mentioned><?oxy_comment_end?> с формантом <c>-ra-</c>, как в <mentioned
                xml:lang="xcl"><lang/>
                <w>nor</w></mentioned>?)</note></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kho"><w>navaka</w>
            <note type="comment">(в сочетании: <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_NTS"/>
                <biblScope>1949 XV 58</biblScope></bibl>)</note></mentioned>, <mentioned
            xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
            <w>nava-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inc-x-old"><lang/>
            <w>nava-</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="cu"><lang/>
            <w>novъ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/>
            <w>новый</w></mentioned>, также <mentioned xml:lang="cu"><lang/>
            <w>novakъ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="pl"><lang/>
            <w>nowak</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sl"><lang/>
            <w>novak</w>
            <gloss><q>юнец</q></gloss>, <gloss><q>новичок</q></gloss> (и <gloss>собств.
            имя</gloss>)</mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lt"><lang/>
            <w>navas</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lt"><lang/>
            <w>naũjas</w></mentioned> (<mentioned xml:lang="ine"><lang/>
            <w type="rec">newyo-</w></mentioned>), <mentioned xml:lang="got"><lang/>
            <w>niujis</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="goh"><lang/>
            <w>niuwi</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/>
            <w>neu</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="xto"><lang/>
            <w>ñu</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="txb"><lang/>
            <w>nuwe</w>, <w>nwe</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sga"><lang/>
            <w>nũë</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="br"><lang/>
            <w>neuez</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/>
            <w>novus</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="grc"><lang/>
            <w>νέος</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="xcl"><lang/>
            <w>nor</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="hit"><lang/>
            <w>newa-</w>
            <gloss><q>новый</q></gloss></mentioned>. Распознается в <mentioned xml:lang="xsc"><lang/>
            <w>Ναυακος</w> (<gloss>собств. имя</gloss>)</mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="xsc"
              ><w>Ναυαγος</w></mentioned> (ср. <mentioned xml:lang="sla"><lang/>
            <w>Novak</w></mentioned>). Простая основа <c>nava-</c>, без форманта <c>-ka-</c>,
          сохранилась в <ref type="xr" target="#entry_næw_1"><w xml:lang="os-x-iron">næw</w>
            <w xml:lang="os-x-digor">næwæ</w>
            <gloss><q>молодая трава</q></gloss>, <gloss><q>дерн</q></gloss></ref>, q. v. См. также
            <ref type="xr" target="#entry_noǵy"/>, <ref type="xr" target="#entry_Nogbon"
              />.<lb/><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_Миллер_Вс._ОЭ"/>
            <biblScope>II 34, 63, 83</biblScope></bibl>; <bibl><ref type="bibl"
              target="#ref_Miller._Gr."/>
            <biblScope>32</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl"
              target="#ref_Hübschmann._Oss."/>
            <biblScope>50</biblScope></bibl>. — <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"/>
            <biblScope>174</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
      </entry>
    </body>
